Hyman, you're gonna 
 break my ear drums.

1943
01:01:53,040 --> 01:01:55,000
- Okay, enjoy it. 
 - Thanks.

1944
01:02:00,920 --> 01:02:04,560
You're young. 
 I'm old and sick.

1945
01:02:04,640 --> 01:02:07,320
What we'll do together 
 in the next few months...

1946
01:02:07,440 --> 01:02:09,480
will make history, Michael.

1947
01:02:09,560 --> 01:02:12,360
History. 
 It's never been done before.

1948
01:02:12,440 --> 01:02:16,600
Not even your father would dream 
 that such a thing could be possible.

1949
01:02:18,680 --> 01:02:21,400
And Pentangeli is a dead man.

1950
01:02:21,520 --> 01:02:24,440
- You don't object? 
 - Pickup of four.

1951
01:02:24,560 --> 01:02:26,360
He's small potatoes.

1952
01:02:36,640 --> 01:02:39,080
What's up?

1953
01:02:41,200 --> 01:02:43,000
We got company, huh?

1954
01:03:21,400 --> 01:03:24,400
Don Corleone, I wish you would've 
 let me know you were comin'.

1955
01:03:24,480 --> 01:03:26,880
I could've prepared 
 something for you.

1956
01:03:27,000 --> 01:03:29,760
I didn't want you to know 
 I was coming.

1957
01:03:35,880 --> 01:03:37,480
You heard what happened 
 in my home?

1958
01:03:37,560 --> 01:03:41,360
- Mike, I almost died myself. 
 - In my home!

1959
01:03:44,680 --> 01:03:47,480
In my bedroom 
 where my wife sleeps!

1960
01:03:50,240 --> 01:03:53,920
Where my children come 
 and play with their toys.

1961
01:03:54,040 --> 01:03:55,840
In my home.

1962
01:04:12,280 --> 01:04:15,200
I want you to help me 
 take my revenge.

1963
01:04:15,320 --> 01:04:17,240
Michael, anything.

1964
01:04:17,360 --> 01:04:19,160
What can I do?

1965
01:04:21,760 --> 01:04:24,960
Settle these troubles 
 with the Rosato brothers.

1966
01:04:25,080 --> 01:04:27,600
Mike, I don't understand. 
 I don't--

1967
01:04:27,680 --> 01:04:30,320
I don't have your brain 
 for big deals...

1968
01:04:30,400 --> 01:04:32,080
but this is a street thing.

1969
