Then why? Why do you ask me 
 to lay down to him, Mike?

1973
01:04:47,440 --> 01:04:50,680
It was Hyman Roth that 
 tried to have me killed.

1974
01:04:52,440 --> 01:04:55,440
I know it was him.

1975
01:04:55,520 --> 01:04:57,800
Jesus Christ, Mike.

1976
01:04:57,880 --> 01:04:59,720
Jesus Christ, look, 
 let's get 'em all.

1977
01:04:59,800 --> 01:05:03,000
Let's hit 'em all now, 
 while we got the muscle.

1978
01:05:07,480 --> 01:05:09,760
This used to be 
 my father's old study.

1979
01:05:11,320 --> 01:05:13,120
It's changed.

1980
01:05:14,480 --> 01:05:16,800
I remember 
 there used to be a--

1981
