A big desk was here.

1982
01:05:21,600 --> 01:05:23,440
I remember when I was a kid, 
 Frankie...

1983
01:05:23,520 --> 01:05:25,840
we had to be very quiet 
 when we played near here.

1984
01:05:33,720 --> 01:05:36,960
I was very happy that this 
 house never went to strangers.

1985
01:05:38,600 --> 01:05:41,640
First Clemenza took it over. 
 Now you.

1986
01:05:44,120 --> 01:05:46,680
My father taught me 
 many things here.

1987
01:05:46,800 --> 01:05:49,080
He taught me in this room.

1988
01:05:52,240 --> 01:05:55,680
He taught me, 
 keep your friends close...

1989
01:05:55,800 --> 01:05:58,000
but your enemies closer.

1990
01:05:58,080 --> 01:06:01,360
Now, if Hyman Roth sees that 
 I interceded in this thing...

1991
01:06:01,440 --> 01:06:04,200
in the Rosato brothers' favor...

1992
01:06:04,280 --> 01:06:07,000
he's gonna think his relationship 
 with me is still good.

1993
01:06:10,320 --> 01:06:13,280
That's what I want him to think.

1994
01:06:13,400 --> 01:06:17,880
I want him completely relaxed 
 and confident in our friendship.

1995
01:06:18,000 --> 01:06:21,720
Then I'll be able to find out 
 who the traitor in my family was.

1996
01:06:48,240 --> 01:06:52,200
- Yeah? 
 - Fredo. This is Johnny.

1997
01:06:52,280 --> 01:06:54,600
Johnny Ola. 
 We need some more help.

1998
01:06:54,680 --> 01:06:56,760
Johnny?

1999
01:06:56,880 --> 01:06:59,640
Jesus Christ, 
 what the hell time is it?

2000
01:06:59,760 --> 01:07:02,600
- Who is that, honey? 
 - Listen good, Fredo.

2001
01:07:02,680 --> 01:07:05,600
What are you callin' me here for? 
 I don't want to talk to you.

2002
01:07:05,720 --> 01:07:07,840
Pentangeli's set up a meeting 
 with the Rosato brothers.

2003
01:07:07,960 --> 01:07:10,200
- He's gonna go for their deal. 
 - Oh, God.

2004
01:07:10,280 --> 01:07:12,720
- Will he come alone? 
 - I don't know anything.

2005
01:07:12,800 --> 01:07:15,280
- You got me in deep enough already. 
 - Just go along.

2006
01:07:15,360 --> 01:07:17,280
Everything will be allright, 
 Fredo.

2007
01:07:17,400 --> 01:07:19,600
Pentangeli says he's 
 willing to make a deal.

2008
01:07:19,680 --> 01:07:22,480
All we wanna know is 
 if he's on the level.

2009
01:07:24,000 --> 01:07:26,920
You guys lied to me. I don't 
 want you to call me anymore.

2010
01:07:27,000 --> 01:07:29,400
Your brother's not gonna 
 find out we talked.

2011
01:07:29,480 --> 01:07:32,280
I don't know 
 what you're talkin' about.

2012
01:07:41,840 --> 01:07:43,640
Who was that?

2013
01:07:43,760 --> 01:07:45,560
Uh, wrong number.

2014
01:07:52,480 --> 01:07:55,280
Frank, I got nobody here.

2015
01:07:55,360 --> 01:07:57,200
- Wait in the car, Cheech. 
 - Frankie--

2016
01:07:57,280 --> 01:07:59,120
It's okay, Cheech.

2017
01:08:05,960 --> 01:08:09,240
- What's this, Rosato? 
 - A lucky "C" note for our new deal.

2018
01:08:12,520 --> 01:08:14,840
Richie. 
 Give us a taste, huh?

2019
01:08:19,320 --> 01:08:23,120
Yeah, we're all real happy 
 about your decision, Frankie.

2020
01:08:23,200 --> 01:08:27,480
- You're not gonna regret it. 
 - I don't like this "C" note.

2021
01:08:27,560 --> 01:08:29,920
I take that as an insult.

2022
01:08:30,040 --> 01:08:32,160
Michael Corleone says hello.

2023
01:08:48,560 --> 01:08:51,520
Get him in! 
 Close the fuckin' door!

2024
01:08:51,640 --> 01:08:53,920
Your friend the cop. 
 What the--

2025
01:08:54,040 --> 01:08:56,640
Hey, Rich, it's dark in here.

2026
01:08:56,760 --> 01:09:00,960
- Are you open or closed? 
 - I just come in to clean up.

2027
01:09:04,200 --> 01:09:06,440
What's the matter?

2028
01:09:06,520 --> 01:09:09,400
- Is that somethin' on the floor? 
 - Carmine, no, no. Not here!

2029
01:09:09,480 --> 01:09:11,840
- Not here! 
 - Not here, Carmine! Not a cop!

2030
01:09:11,960 --> 01:09:13,760
What?

2031
01:09:13,880 --> 01:09:17,200
You open your fuckin' mouth, 
 I'll blow your head off!

2032
01:10:01,280 --> 01:10:03,120
Freddie. Good to see ya.

2033
01:10:05,880 --> 01:10:07,720
Where is he?

2034
01:10:07,800 --> 01:10:10,360
He's okay. He's in the back.

2035
01:10:14,200 --> 01:10:16,520
Come on, girls. 
 Take a hike, huh?

2036
01:10:19,480 --> 01:10:21,320
In this room here.

