- Listen, Hagen, I did not-- 
 - No.

2041
01:10:48,360 --> 01:10:50,320
- It's all right. 
 - I didn't do anything.

2042
01:10:50,440 --> 01:10:52,480
It's okay.

2043
01:10:52,600 --> 01:10:54,760
You're very lucky.

2044
01:10:54,840 --> 01:10:57,240
My brother Fredo 
 operates this place.

2045
01:10:57,320 --> 01:11:00,000
He was called before anyone.

2046
01:11:00,120 --> 01:11:01,760
Now, if this had happened 
 someplace else...

2047
01:11:01,880 --> 01:11:02,880
we couldn't 
 have helped you.

2048
01:11:06,800 --> 01:11:11,040
When I woke up 
 I was on the floor...

2049
01:11:11,160 --> 01:11:12,960
and I don't know 
 how it happened.

2050
01:11:13,080 --> 01:11:14,880
You can't remember?

2051
01:11:18,480 --> 01:11:20,400
I passed out.

2052
01:11:26,080 --> 01:11:27,920
I'll fix it.

2053
01:11:28,000 --> 01:11:29,880
Okay.

2054
01:11:35,800 --> 01:11:37,920
It was just a game.

2055
01:11:38,040 --> 01:11:39,360
Jesus.

2056
01:11:42,040 --> 01:11:43,840
Oh.

2057
01:11:49,080 --> 01:11:51,120
Jesus! Jesus!

2058
01:11:55,400 --> 01:11:58,000
Jesus God.

2059
01:11:58,120 --> 01:11:59,960
Oh, God.

2060
01:12:02,200 --> 01:12:05,760
I don't know and I don't 
 understand why I can't remember.

2061
01:12:05,880 --> 01:12:08,600
You don't have to remember. 
 Just do as I say.

2062
01:12:08,680 --> 01:12:11,160
They're putting a call in 
 to your office.

2063
01:12:11,280 --> 01:12:15,040
Explain that you'll be there 
 tomorrow afternoon.

2064
01:12:15,160 --> 01:12:17,200
You decided to spend the night...

2065
01:12:17,280 --> 01:12:21,040
at Michael Corleone's house 
 in Tahoe as his guest.

2066
01:12:21,720 --> 01:12:24,480
I do remember 
 that she was laughing.

2067
01:12:26,360 --> 01:12:28,200
We'd done it before...

2068
01:12:28,280 --> 01:12:31,480
and I know that I could 
 not have hurt that girl.

2069
01:12:32,600 --> 01:12:34,400
This girl has no family.

2070
01:12:34,520 --> 01:12:36,400
Nobody knows 
 that she worked here.

2071
01:12:36,520 --> 01:12:38,880
It'll be as though 
 she never existed.

2072
01:12:41,480 --> 01:12:43,800
All that's left 
 is our friendship.

2073
01:12:58,840 --> 01:13:00,680
- Yes? 
 - I'm sorry, Mrs. Corleone.

2074
01:13:00,760 --> 01:13:04,560
- We're not to let you through. 
 - I'm just going to the market.

2075
01:13:04,680 --> 01:13:07,120
Well, if you'll just give us a list, 
 we'll pick up anything you want.

2076
01:13:07,240 --> 01:13:10,320
- Whose orders are these? 
 - Mr. Hagen's, ma'am. He's coming.

2077
01:13:10,440 --> 01:13:13,440
All right, well, I'm just gonna 
 have to speak to Mr. Hagen.

2078
01:13:18,560 --> 01:13:22,000
I wanted to explain this, but 
 I had business in Carson City.

2079
01:13:22,120 --> 01:13:24,080
Now, this is Michael's 
 request for your safety.

2080
01:13:24,160 --> 01:13:26,640
- We can send out for anything. 
 - I see.

2081
01:13:26,760 --> 01:13:28,640
I'm supposed to stay 
 in my house.

2082
01:13:28,760 --> 01:13:31,120
No, within the compound 
 would be fine.

2083
01:13:31,240 --> 01:13:33,400
I was going to take the children 
 to New England next week.

2084
01:13:33,520 --> 01:13:36,600
- That's off now. 
 - Am I a prisoner? Is that it?

2085
01:13:36,720 --> 01:13:39,080
- That's not the way we look at it. 
 - All right, come on, kids.

2086
01:13:39,160 --> 01:13:41,000
We're going back to the house.

2087
01:13:43,280 --> 01:13:45,080
Joe.

